  <entry>
    <title>我的小站也可以评论啦</title>
    <link href="https://hi.laotou.icu/2021/08/17/11/"/>
    <id>https://hi.laotou.icu/2021/08/17/11/</id>
    <published>2021-08-17T13:17:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-27T15:13:02.470Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>  话说我看到别人家的博客都有评论的系统，但是咱的小站就没有这个评论系统，后来我也网上搜了一些资料，但是就咱的文化水平，感觉看起来就是一《天书》啊！</p><span id="more"></span><p>其实在网上搜的时候，咱一直把关键词定在《gitalk》这个关键词了，虽然网上的教程不少，但是对于我这种没啥文化的人来说，只能是一知半解的懵逼状态中浏览和摸索，直到我把关键词里加入了我使用的主题名字《fluid》，正巧看到《fluid主题配置》这篇文章。《PS：fluid主题虽然支持：<strong>disqus | gitalk | valine | waline | changyan | livere | remark42 | twikoo | cusdis</strong>  等众多评论系统，但是我文化低啊，根本不会自己弄啊，尤其是看hexo帮助文件，更加感觉是一部天书无疑。》</p><p>fluid主题增加gitalk评论系统的链接如下：</p><p><a class="link"   href="https://atroxqw.github.io/posts/2020/12/31/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/#7-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-gitalk" >https://atroxqw.github.io/posts/2020/12/31/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/#7-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-gitalk<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><p>这个正是我要找的，🤭，这种教程正好对应我这种没啥文化的人的操作。</p><p>所以我直接复制该作者的《集成评论功能gitalk》这一段教程。</p><p>教程如下：</p><hr><h3 id="集成评论功能-gitalk"><a href="#集成评论功能-gitalk" class="headerlink" title="集成评论功能(gitalk)"></a>集成评论功能(gitalk)</h3><h4 id="7-1-注册OAuth-Application"><a href="#7-1-注册OAuth-Application" class="headerlink" title="7.1 注册OAuth Application"></a>7.1 注册OAuth Application</h4><p><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new" >官方入口<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>，点击进入来<strong>注册一个新的OAuth Application</strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/new_application.png"><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/new_application.png"                      alt="注册OAuth Application"                >注册OAuth Application</a></p><h4 id="7-2-注册后获取秘钥"><a href="#7-2-注册后获取秘钥" class="headerlink" title="7.2 注册后获取秘钥"></a>7.2 注册后获取秘钥</h4><p>点击注册后，会进入新页面。显示我们的OAuth <strong>Application</strong>的 <strong>Client ID</strong> 和 尚未生成的 <strong>Client secrets</strong></p><p>，点击 <strong>Generate a new client secret</strong> 按钮生成秘钥即可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Client_id_secrets.png"><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Client_id_secrets.png"                      alt="获取秘钥"                ></a></p><p><a class="link"   href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Client_id_secrets.png" >获取秘钥<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><h4 id="7-3-博客集成gitalk"><a href="#7-3-博客集成gitalk" class="headerlink" title="7.3 博客集成gitalk"></a>7.3 博客集成gitalk</h4><p>在<code>_config.fluid.yml</code>中<strong>开启并指定评论模块</strong>。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post:</span><br><span class="line">  comments:</span><br><span class="line">    enable: true</span><br><span class="line">    type: gitalk</span><br><span class="line">Copy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在下方还要设<strong>置对应评论模块的参数</strong>:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">  clientID: af550312a411b96c64b9     #刚才的ClientID</span><br><span class="line">  clientSecret: f11934265fd18324cb2d9fd605d7d445207a3e52   #刚才的clientSecret</span><br><span class="line">  repo: &#x27;gitalk&#x27;                                     #刚才取的名</span><br><span class="line">  owner: &#x27;AtroxQW&#x27;                            #github的用户名</span><br><span class="line">  admin: [&#x27;AtroxQW&#x27;]</span><br><span class="line">  language: zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">  labels: [&#x27;Gitalk&#x27;]</span><br><span class="line">  perPage: 10</span><br><span class="line">  pagerDirection: last</span><br><span class="line">  distractionFreeMode: false</span><br><span class="line">  createIssueManually: true</span><br><span class="line">Copy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="7-4-初始化issue"><a href="#7-4-初始化issue" class="headerlink" title="7.4 初始化issue"></a>7.4 初始化issue</h4><p>每次发表一篇博客，都需要我们作者<strong>初始化issue</strong>，初始化后评论就会在github上看到。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/init_issue.png"><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AtroxQW/jsDeliverCDN@1.0/source/_posts/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/init_issue.png"                      alt="初始化issue"                >初始化issue</a></p><hr><p>同时感谢该作者的分享哈，最后放上该作者的博文链接：</p><p><a class="link"   href="https://atroxqw.github.io/posts/2020/12/31/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/#7-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-gitalk" >https://atroxqw.github.io/posts/2020/12/31/fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/#7-%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-gitalk<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;  话说我看到别人家的博客都有评论的系统，但是咱的小站就没有这个评论系统，后来我也网上搜了一些资料，但是就咱的文化水平，感觉看起来就是一《天书》啊！&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
